dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. In upper left corner: Keith Johnston's general atlas. Printed in blue and black, with hand coloring indicating administrative boundaries. Inset: Islands of Japan. In upper right corner: 34. Originally issued folded in cover 24 x 11 cm.
